				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">My CPU loop (skeleton underneath) is pretty standard:
<br />- get opcode, decrement cpu cycles
<br />
<br />- update dmc, framesequencer, and mapper irq
<br />
<br />- run opcode
<br />PPU, APU, mapper hardware get updated here if they are written to.
<br />
<br />- run interrupt
<br />If any irq was first set at the last cycle of the current opcode, the interrupt handler will instead be called after the next opcode.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

